  ('dietitian-moex-02982', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-103-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關肌酸酐／身高指數（creatinine height index, CHI）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["評估體內瘦肌肉群（lean body mass）的方法之一", "當受測者營養不良，體蛋白耗損時，CHI值會下降", "腎功能不全的患者，不適合用CHI來評估營養狀況", "CHI%＝（受測者24小時血液中肌酸酐含量（mg）／同性別、同身高24小時血液中肌酸酐標準量（mg））×100"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "eb0f58c00a5d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "c5065c861ddd", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "103030", "c": "106", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "103", "exam_name": "103年第一次專技醫師中醫師分階段考試、中醫師營養師心理師護理師社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
